    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classMeshEntry" kindref="compound">MeshEntry</ref> is a single &apos;compartment&apos; in the mathematical sense, that is, all properties are assumed homogenous within it. It is a <ref refid="classFieldElement" kindref="compound">FieldElement</ref>, so it gets all its values from the parent <ref refid="classChemCompt" kindref="compound">ChemCompt</ref>. </para>
